  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Sleight of Hand 3 ranks, Telekinesis sphere, Mind Limb.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> You can use your telekinetic limb to perform steal combat maneuvers and make Sleight of Hand checks to hide an object, palm a weapon, or take something unnoticed. Perception checks to notice you doing so take a penalty equal to half your character level, and when you successfully perform a steal combat maneuver or take something unnoticed you may make a Sleight of Hand check to hide it as a free action.</p>\n<p><strong>Special:</strong> If you have the Aggressive Mind Limb feat, you may use your additional attack of opportunity with your mind limb to attempt a steal combat maneuver.</p>\n",
